  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13052247/lakes-chalet-hotel.jpg" alt="Our Chalet Hotels" data-udi="umb://media/0ded13d4bfab4995b8062a5633e9ad26" /></p>
<p>Since their introduction to our summer programme, Inghams Chalet Hotels have become established favourites with our Lakes &amp; Mountains guests. All are run by our own carefully selected teams of Inghams staff, and provide a friendly and welcoming ‘home from home’ ambience combined with excellent value for money on our ‘Half Board PLUS’ arrangements.</p>
<p>As you can see from the resort choices set out below, most of our properties are in wonderful mountain walking resorts, from the Austrian Tyrol to the Italian Dolomites, and the French Savoie Alps.</p>
<p><strong>Chalet Ratings</strong></p>
<p>The ratings shown for each property are our own ratings and are not to be confused or compared with any system of official 'star' ratings or hotel categories. As <a data-udi="umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bfe7675d92e4c888cf5dee0c78eb888}" title="Chalet Hotel">Chalet Hotels</a> have no official ratings, our ratings are based on senior management inspections, coupled with any guest feedback where available. To help you with your chalet and Chalet Hotel choice, we show our star rating as a guide to help you compare between our Chalet Hotels as follows: <br /><br /><strong>◆ ◆ ◆ </strong>Simple but comfortable, offering excellent value for money.<br /><strong>◆ ◆ ◆ ◆</strong> Superior levels of style and comfort in all living areas and generally with en suite bathroom facilities.<br /><strong>◆ ◆ ◆ ◆ ◆</strong> Our top properties in terms of style, comfort and facilities.</p>
<p>An additional half ◇ is added to indicate something special within its grade, such as a private sauna or hot tub, a fantastic location, sensational views or use of a swimming pool.</p>
